com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface Polygon

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Geometry

    public interface Polygon
extends Geometry
    This interface represents the <Polygon> tag from KML specification. A Polygon is defined by an outer boundary.

    • Field Summary

      This constant defines an XML attribute defining any cutout elements of the <Polygon>.
      static java.lang.String OUTER_BOUNDARY
      This constant defines am XML attribute defining the outer edge of the <Polygon>.
